  "description": [
    "HEADERS CLEARING HOUSE Cobblor Sauce And Query Mrs L M C Arlington Tor Mrs M L C Os Wash Ington I am happy to be able to aupply the recipe for creamy white sauce which your mother ate on apple cobbler when a child So did I and I still make it Take as much nollk as you wish add a little top milk if desired sweeten to taste thicken with cornstarch mixed with a little water to make a paste cook until proper con sistency You can guage your proportions Season with nut meg or vanilla When made thicker this also makes a nice filling for layer cake Mrs J M J SUver Spring I dont have a recipe for the sauce for apple cobbler your mother wanted but I would love to have your mothers apple cobbler recipe I am looking for a good one Flower Reiresher Mrs C M K Washington Recently someone wrote in May Day Parties Continued From Page B4 daughter Mrs Jack Kennedy without her Senator husband the Walter Louchheims Mr Clarence Hewes who had also been at the Burtons party and Mrs Eldridge Jordan Southern Visitor Mr and Mrs Herbert Pales were there"
